sentence: Last month, when Stefanik endorsed a primary opponent of Rep. Liz Cheney of Wyoming, whose GOP leadership post she now holds, Stefanik went above and beyond to turn the knife.
title: Elise Stefanik is the human embodiment of how the GOP went down the tubes
